Description of incident: Tower Club is taking steps to              protect 103 of its alumni in the classes of 2006 and 2007 after a              spreadsheet listing their names and Social Security numbers was e-mailed              to current club members. The document was attached to an apparently              unrelated e-mail that informed current members about a club event.              The spreadsheet was attached unintentionally because of a technical              glitch in an email program.
